data.description: Ready for your own Hobby Farm in highly desirable New Haven/Gray/Ryle school district with low Boone county taxes?! This property is looking for its next owner featuring +/- 4.097 ac, 4 stall 36x36 horse barn with electric and water, fenced pastures, 3 car oversized garage with 2 attached to the house built on a permanent, full basement with ample storage! The open and split bedroom floor plan, gracious room sizes and lovely kitchen with custom wood cabinetry won't disappoint! All this plus more only minutes to shopping, dining & highway!
